snippet.title: IREM Arcade Hits Trailer (Official)
snippet.description:
official website : http://www.irem-arcade-hits.com
Irem Arcade Hits is the ultimate compilation of Irem coin-op games, released on December 9th 2010. It includes 18 blockbuster games such as R-Type Leo, Kung-Fu Master, In The Hunt, Hammerin' Harry, Vigilante and much more.

UPDATE : IREM Arcade Hits is now available on the Mac App Store ! http://bit.ly/pqiVqd
